Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:19.91,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't supposed to be like this, head in my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.37,0:00:26.25,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Struggling to escape from this saturated world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:32.01,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Time passes like whispering sand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.55,0:00:35.72,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,These circumstances, unchanging
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.72,0:00:38.72,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,gazing out at a dreamless tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.64,0:00:45.81,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna say goodbye to the confusion of yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.19,0:00:51.23,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,I try reaching out, as if to resist
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.53,0:00:56.95,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,We cry millions of times and then get born again
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.24,0:01:00.16,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go with these red eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.16,0:01:03.37,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,to that pictured future
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.37,0:01:08.96,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Come here right by me, I'm clapping my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.13,0:01:11.05,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.05,0:01:15.42,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Strain my eyes in the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.42,0:01:21.06,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Can't see anything, don't know anything, but I'll still go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.31,0:01:27.39,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,To the place of shining light in which you wait
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.39,0:01:29.98,Episode Num,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 3
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.39,0:01:29.98,Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Masked{\b0} Mansion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.39,0:01:29.98,Source,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Inspired by Ango Sakaguchi’s\NMeijikaika Ango Torimonochou\N(Meiji-era Ango Detective Stories)\N"Masked Mansion" and "Shoplifting Family"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.95,0:01:39.75,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm home already.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.79,0:01:42.04,Name White,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)\a5}Sasa Kigihiko
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.79,0:01:42.04,Name Sub White,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)\a5}Younger Brother of the Late Sasa Komamori
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.75,0:01:42.04,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,We'll discuss the property issue \Nduring tomorrow's meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.04,0:01:43.87,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,President Kazamori?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.87,0:01:47.29,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,Even though the company's in his name, \Nit was originally the Sasa family's.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.29,0:01:50.01,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to tell \NKazamori every little thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.05,0:01:52.67,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(500,0)}Uncle Kigihiko, the materials on the property matter are prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.14,0:01:58.97,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Kazamori Holdings\NReal Estate Sale Proposal\NPresident Sasa Kazamori
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.22,0:02:02.48,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kazamori, it's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.48,0:02:04.85,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't intend to leave you out \Nand make the decision on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:07.52,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,Can I go over there now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.48,0:02:10.11,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Not necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:14.61,Name White,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,0)\b1}Sasa{\b0} Fumihiko
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:14.61,Name White,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,0)}Son of the Late Sasa Komamori
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:14.61,Name White,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,0)\b1\a5}Sasa{\b0} Itoji
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:14.61,Name White,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,0)\a5}Widow of the Late Sasa Komamori
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.32,0:02:20.24,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,Kigihiko-san, the praying \Nis about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:23.41,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sister, I was going to see Kazamori...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.41,0:02:27.13,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,That man won't come anyway. \NLet's go, Fumihiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.13,0:02:28.13,Main Dialog,Fumihiko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.59,0:02:35.09,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,My dear departed husband, Komamori...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.09,0:02:37.55,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,Please watch over us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.55,0:02:40.01,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,Please protect the Sasa family.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.39,0:02:43.98,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,Seven years ago today, you \Nwere tragically killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.98,0:02:46.52,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,The Sasa family has \Ncontinued to thrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:49.69,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,My dear departed husband, Komamori...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.69,0:02:51.40,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,My dear departed husband, Komamori...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:52.19,Main Dialog,Fumihiko,0000,0000,0000,,Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.19,0:02:54.15,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:57.16,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,Brother? You're referring \Nto Kazamori-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.49,0:03:01.91,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We{\i0} are Komamori's blood relatives. \NNo one else is needed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.79,0:03:08.08,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Adopted son or not, Kazamori \Nis the head of this family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:08.25,Name,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)\b1\a5}Sasa{\b0} Mitsuko
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:08.25,Name Sub,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)\a5}Daughter of the Late Sasa Komamori
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:10.04,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,We should be together, at least on \Nthe anniversary of Father's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:13.88,Main Dialog,Fumihiko,0000,0000,0000,,That guy likes to close himself \Noff from everyone, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:18.30,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:19.64,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,I already told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.64,0:03:22.85,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,Kazamori-san is sick, so don't \Njust go running over to the annex!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.73,0:03:27.23,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,My dear departed husband, Komamori...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.23,0:03:29.31,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,Fumihiko, your child by blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:33.69,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,is graduating university and will \Njoin the business in the spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:35.36,Main Dialog,Fumihiko,0000,0000,0000,,Blackout?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:56.17,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kazamori?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.80,0:03:57.76,Name White,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,0)\a5\b1}Sasa{\b0} Kazamori
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.80,0:03:57.76,Name Sub White,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,0)\a5}Adopted Son of the Late Komamori Sasa\NCurrent Head of the Family
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.18,0:04:01.09,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness. I thought maybe \Nsomething happened to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.09,0:04:04.51,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you haven't shown your face \Nin a long, long time, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:10.60,Main Dialog,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,Kazamori-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.65,0:04:12.02,Name White,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,0)\b1}Taku{\b0} Hidenobu
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.65,0:04:12.02,Name Sub White,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,0)}Live-in Doctor {ditto from note above}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:12.61,Main Dialog,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,Quickly, get inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:34.42,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,Kazamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:36.67,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Did something happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:37.76,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,Kazamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:40.13,Main Dialog,Fumihiko,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.97,0:04:42.43,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Kazamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:46.77,Main Dialog,Fumihiko,0000,0000,0000,,This is just like seven \Nyears ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.64,0:04:44.68,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Kazamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.65,0:04:56.48,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Taku! What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:57.73,Main Dialog,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,Kazamori-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:04:58.82,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,Kazamori?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.82,0:04:59.86,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,That's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:03.99,Main Dialog,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,When I got there, Kazamori-kun \Nwas on fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.99,0:05:04.74,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,Mitchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:12.92,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that can be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.92,0:05:13.79,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,Kazamori-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:16.46,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,Kazamori-san! Kazamori-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.34,0:05:19.55,Main Dialog,Fumihiko,0000,0000,0000,,It's a curse...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.76,0:05:25.35,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! This is \Nmy husband's curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:29.93,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,I see... It's the anniversary \Nof my brother's death...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:31.69,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,A curse...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.19,0:05:34.56,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.48,0:05:38.23,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Shinjuku Station
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:46.49,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,No Trespassing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:06:03.13,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Restricted area admittance \Nguards, you're doing a fine job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:02.92,Name White,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)\b1\a5}Kaishou{\b0} Rie
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:02.92,Name Sub White,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)\a5}Kaishou Rinroku's Daughter\NLives at Home
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:09.47,Main Dialog,Photographer1,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? An explosion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:11.10,Main Dialog,Photographer1,0000,0000,0000,,Are we okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:13.44,Main Dialog,Photographer1,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shit! Oh, shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.57,0:06:21.94,Main Dialog Italic,Newscaster,0000,0000,0000,,An amendment to the \NSelf-Defense Forces Act,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.57,0:06:24.57,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26}Possibility that preemptive self-defense measures will be invoked\NNew guidelines to Self-Defense Forces pushed through
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:23.70,Main Dialog Italic,Newscaster,0000,0000,0000,,allowing the use of military \Nforce against terrorist forces,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.70,0:06:26.53,Main Dialog Italic,Newscaster,0000,0000,0000,,was passed unanimously in the \NHouse of Representatives today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:30.45,Main Dialog Italic,Newscaster,0000,0000,0000,,Because of the emergency, it is due \Nto go into effect three days from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:34.04,Main Dialog Italic,Newscaster,0000,0000,0000,,Herewith, all Self-Defense Forces \Nthat are already deployed abroad
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:37.17,Main Dialog Italic,Newscaster,0000,0000,0000,,on peacekeeping missions may \Nparticipate in combat activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.60,0:06:58.44,Name White,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,0)\b1}In{\b0}ga
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.60,0:06:58.44,Name Sub White,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,0)}Detective's Assistant
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:25.84,Main Dialog Italic,Mascot,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be too rough. Handle me gently!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.18,0:07:28.72,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Shinjurou!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:35.56,Name White,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)\b1}Yuuki{\b0} Shinjurou
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:35.56,Name Sub White,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}Detective
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:36.73,Main Dialog,Old Man,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.15,0:07:43.36,Main Dialog Italic,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:44.86,Main Dialog Italic,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:07:59.29,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,It's not connecting...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:01.67,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Or more like, the connection \Nis being rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.67,0:08:02.84,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Shinjurou!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:09.51,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.51,0:08:10.89,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,It's talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.89,0:08:15.64,Main Dialog,Mascot,0000,0000,0000,,A stocking... Hosiery...Called \Nhold-ups in Britain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:16.93,Main Dialog,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.93,0:08:19.31,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,It just uses a chip like the kind \Nused in old video game machines
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:21.77,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,to pick up vocabulary off the net.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.77,0:08:23.06,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have any others?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.06,0:08:26.57,Main Dialog,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,I gave all my customers the \Ne-mail address for that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.57,0:08:28.45,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Customers... You mean your...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:31.03,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.62,0:08:34.53,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you use mail \Nto haggle over the price too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:38.21,Main Dialog,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,After all, if he's a nice \Nguy, I give him a discount.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.21,0:08:41.21,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,All of the mail functions \Nare code-checked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.67,0:08:45.34,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Possible terrorist and \Nlikely illegal exchanges
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.34,0:08:47.42,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,are pinpointed and access is cut off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.88,0:08:50.22,Main Dialog,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Do something, Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.22,0:08:52.64,Main Dialog,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,You're an acquaintance of \NChairman Kaishou, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.93,0:08:54.60,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,The Defeated Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:57.35,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,In the middle of a losing record \Nagainst Chairman Kaishou!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:09:00.89,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,The guy is top-of-the-heap elite,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:03.77,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,an information analysis adviser \Nto the military and police,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:04.98,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,with a grip on the \Ncommunication net as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:09.53,Main Dialog,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,But at this rate, I'll \Nlose all my customers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.28,0:09:13.82,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Shinjurou! Horsies!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.62,0:09:17.58,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuki Shinjurou!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.58,0:09:20.04,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,I want to consult you about a case!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.50,0:09:22.92,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like it'd be a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.92,0:09:23.75,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:25.92,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten me? It's Rie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:27.17,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Kaishou Rie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.17,0:09:28.55,Main Dialog,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Kaishou?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.55,0:09:29.84,Main Dialog,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Is she...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.48,0:09:50.74,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,On one condition!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.33,0:09:58.91,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to use your \Nold man's connections
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.91,0:10:01.87,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,to reconnect a certain smartphone line.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:02.62,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:10.67,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Why horses?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:13.93,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that it was forbidden \Nto live in this zone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.93,0:10:14.55,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Come again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.18,0:10:19.60,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Ordinance says no one can \Nenter by vehicle or on foot,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.60,0:10:22.14,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,but there's nothing in there \Nabout riding in on a horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.14,0:10:23.89,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Clever, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.89,0:10:26.90,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the daughter of Kaishou Rinroku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.90,0:10:28.32,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,I can't break the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:29.77,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:31.11,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:33.65,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Inga!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:35.07,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Inga?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.07,0:10:36.74,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Inga that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:41.95,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Are you that woman's little brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:52.96,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,This is Mitsuko, the younger sister \Nof Sasa Kazamori, who passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:58.22,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,She contacted my father soon \Nafter it happened last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:11:04.02,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted Chairman Kaishou to prove \Nthat Brother didn't die from a curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.27,0:11:05.44,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,A curse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.94,0:11:06.65,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.94,0:11:08.86,Main Dialog,Fumihiko,0000,0000,0000,,It's a curse...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:13.65,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,A curse? Who would do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:16.70,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,They think it's a curse \Nfrom my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:19.70,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know of my \Nfather, Sasa Komamori?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.70,0:11:21.41,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,I sure don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.79,0:11:24.75,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm not really familiar either...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:27.25,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it was all over the news?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:30.25,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't in this country at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.05,0:11:37.43,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sasa Komamori was a researcher in \Nthe field of artificial intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:41.22,Main Dialog,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond human intelligence
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:43.97,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,Sasa Komamori was a true genius
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:46.81,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,who created a device for entertainment
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.81,0:11:48.77,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,that could even pass the Turing Test.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:52.32,Name,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,0)\b1}Sasa{\b0} Komamori
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:52.32,Name Sub,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,0)}Developer of RAI
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:52.32,Main Dialog,Koyama,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't he also a kook who wore \Na mask in front of other people?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:56.70,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,He used to say it was to hide his \Nblushing face whenever he met someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.70,0:11:59.07,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,but I suspected it was his character.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.07,0:12:05.58,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,But seven years after Komamori-san died \Nlike that, Kazamori-kun followed him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:03.08,Name White,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,0)\b1}Kaishou{\b0} Rinroku
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:03.08,Name Sub White,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,0)}Chairman of JJ Systems
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:03.08,Name White,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,0)\a5\b1}Koyama{\b0} Izumi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:03.08,Name Sub White,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,0)\a5}Public Prosecutor\N Joint Coordinating Dept.\N Public Prosecutor's Office
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:09.33,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I know about RAI.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:12.17,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,A program that duplicates human thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:14.84,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Purpose-built bodies were \Nsold too, weren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:20.89,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,But my father's invention became \Nillegal under the new legislation,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.89,0:12:25.22,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,and during wartime, the prosecutor's \Noffice suddenly began making raids.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.60,0:12:26.98,Main Dialog,Detective,0000,0000,0000,,Sasa Komamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.98,0:12:29.98,Main Dialog,Detective,0000,0000,0000,,Your research is suspected \Nof being a flagrant violation
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.98,0:12:32.15,Main Dialog,Detective,0000,0000,0000,,of the New Information \NPrivacy and Protection Act!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.15,0:12:33.40,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.40,0:12:36.57,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,This whole country has gone insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.57,0:12:41.36,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,Don't they know how much Sasa Komamori \Nhas contributed to the world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.58,0:12:47.33,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kazamori?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.29,0:12:50.25,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Are you with Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:02.22,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:07.27,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,An explosion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.27,0:13:08.22,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.06,0:13:12.31,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,After Father's remains were found \Nat the site of the explosion,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:14.61,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,the vast fortune he left \Nbehind and his company
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.61,0:13:17.73,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,were inherited by Kazamori.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:21.24,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Why would "Brother" be \Ncursed by Sasa Komamori?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.36,0:13:23.87,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,One day, Kazamori
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.37,0:13:27.62,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,was suddenly brought to \Nthis house by Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:31.41,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,The child was distantly \Nrelated to Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:35.59,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Father had adopted him, \Nand as his heir at that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.84,0:13:37.80,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,The adopted son became the heir?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:40.22,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,From the beginning, the \Nsuccessor of the Sasa family
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.22,0:13:41.84,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,wore a mask as proof of his position.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:45.01,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Mask?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.22,0:13:53.06,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,So I've never seen his true face...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:55.23,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,And now I'll never be able to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.36,0:13:58.57,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,On the anniversary of the \Ndeath of Sasa Komamori,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.57,0:14:01.49,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,his heir died the same \Nway, engulfed in flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.95,0:14:04.95,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,You don't think a curse \Nis involved, Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:10.25,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,This is my uncle, Kigihiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.58,0:14:15.00,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,Kazamori never showed his \Nface at the company either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:17.25,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,He was president in name only,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.25,0:14:19.42,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,while he had my sister-in-law \Nand me run the whole group.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:24.76,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Brother was only socially \Nawkward because of that mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:27.30,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,He made decisions on all \Nof the important issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:38.98,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Fumihiko, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:44.53,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,As Kazamori-san is no longer with us, \NFumihiko is the new head of the household.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:47.99,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, I know you're the \Ndaughter of Chairman Kaishou,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:51.41,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,but bringing a detective \Nhere is discourteous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:55.33,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. Do you really think \Na curse was at work here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.33,0:14:57.79,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, it was only \Na figure of speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:15:01.00,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,Kazamori-san was so shocked \Nby the death of my husband
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:04.01,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,that his equilibrium had been \Ndisturbed these past seven years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.01,0:15:07.64,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,Such that he always required \NDr. Taku to be at his side.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.01,0:15:10.10,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Where is this Dr. Taku?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.10,0:15:12.89,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,The doctor is at rest, \Nrecovering from his burns.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:19.81,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,My husband's death caused Kazamori-san \Nno end of anguish, like a curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.81,0:15:21.57,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,He reached his breaking point
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.57,0:15:24.24,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,and chose the same method \Nof dying as my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.24,0:15:25.15,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:27.91,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kazamori did not commit suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.91,0:15:29.16,Main Dialog,Fumihiko,0000,0000,0000,,Then why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:33.16,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Brother knew something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.71,0:15:39.46,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,He tried to warn me about \Nsome kind of imminent danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:41.25,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Just like seven years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:44.71,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,He was prepared to commit suicide, \Nso he told you to get away, Mitchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:45.72,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:50.60,Name White,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,0)\b1}Hayami{\b0} Seigen
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:50.60,Name Sub White,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,0)}Director of the Security Bureau \NMetropolitan Police Dept.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.05,0:15:52.35,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.35,0:15:55.10,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.35,0:15:57.31,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,I asked him to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.77,0:16:00.10,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,After hearing that my father \Nentrusted you with his deductions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.86,0:16:03.07,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,Chairman Kaishou's deductions...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.07,0:16:06.86,Main Dialog,Fumihiko,0000,0000,0000,,I heard he can figure out any mystery \Nwithout even going to the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.45,0:16:13.24,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,If my father is going to lie again \Nto protect some big whatever,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:14.29,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to stand for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:15.87,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:18.92,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you what the \NChairman surmised.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.92,0:16:20.12,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:26.34,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,Mask aside, Kazamori-kun was an \Nintellectual, level-headed top executive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:29.18,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,It's unthinkable he would be so \Nobsessed with his father's death
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.18,0:16:30.26,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,that he would commit suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:33.68,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Still, he could have decided \Nto do it on a sudden impulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:36.77,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, why wouldn't he copy his \Nfather's death, down to the explosion?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:41.44,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,I sense a design binding Kazamori-kun's \Ndeath to that of the Late Komamori.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.44,0:16:42.77,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,This was murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.77,0:16:44.32,Main Dialog,Fumihiko,0000,0000,0000,,Murder?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.61,0:16:47.94,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Aside from the victim, there \Nwere five people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:52.20,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,The victim's stepmother, Sasa Itoji.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:55.41,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,The victim's uncle, Sasa Kigihiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:16:59.46,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,The victim's step-siblings, \NMitsuko and Fumihiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.46,0:17:01.79,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,And Dr. Taku Hidenobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:05.59,Main Dialog,Fumihiko,0000,0000,0000,,Huh! Both Sis and I are suspects!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.55,0:17:10.51,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Due to the death of Kazamori, Fumihiko \Nis now the successor to the business,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.51,0:17:13.22,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,as well as the head of \Nthe Sasa household.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:15.30,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,As such, we could say \Nhe had the most to gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.68,0:17:17.10,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.10,0:17:20.48,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Fumihiko came out of his \Nroom after I left mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.48,0:17:23.48,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Chairman Kaishou has also \Nsaid that it was unthinkable
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:24.69,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,for Fumihiko to have a hand in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.27,0:17:29.32,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,There was a time when Sasa \NKigihiko helped Komamori
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.32,0:17:31.36,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,and he does know a lot about \Nmechanical engineering.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:33.61,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,It would have been simple for him \Nto have rigged a cable or something
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:36.83,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,in the room, decide on a time, cause \Na short, and then have it catch fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:40.71,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,But even with Mr. Kazamori dead, \NKigihiko wouldn't get the inheritance...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.96,0:17:44.33,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the one that most wants \NFumihiko to inherit the company?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.67,0:17:47.71,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,The mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.43,0:17:56.05,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,You're accusing me of asking Kigihiko \Nto murder for Fumihiko's sake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.05,0:17:56.72,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,How disrespectful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:17:59.14,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,What do you make of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.52,0:18:02.48,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:04.31,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:06.73,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't kill Kazamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.73,0:18:08.19,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we could've killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.19,0:18:09.11,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,Kigihiko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.36,0:18:11.49,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,No way you could've... killed him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.49,0:18:13.70,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,We have to tell him, Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.70,0:18:15.07,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, we'll be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:16.57,Main Dialog,Hayami,0000,0000,0000,,We'll continue this in \Nan interrogation room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.00,0:18:24.75,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,A surveillance camera...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:26.25,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:30.00,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,Kazamori must have set up surveillance \Ncameras all over the house
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:32.38,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,and watched every move we made!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:33.51,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.72,0:18:35.34,Main Dialog,Hayami,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.86,0:18:52.53,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Shinjurou...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.57,0:18:55.57,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is swirling around...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:18:58.53,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Now is okay, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:18:59.66,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Inga!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:01.70,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:19.55,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:22.68,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Whom should I ask, and what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.94,0:19:35.65,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,It's all recorded.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:37.36,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how far you go back,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:40.07,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,you're not going to find footage of \Nme setting anything up in this room!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.07,0:19:41.58,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,Check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.58,0:19:44.08,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, he committed suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.50,0:19:46.21,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.68,0:19:59.55,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,That woman again...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.26,0:20:02.68,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.10,0:20:04.60,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,My boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:07.02,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,She wants to ask you a \Nquestion or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.06,0:20:10.94,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Built-in computer...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.32,0:20:13.98,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:17.70,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Who is Sasa Kazamori?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.49,0:20:21.57,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Whose face is it under the mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.95,0:20:25.37,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Someone was posing as Kazamori?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.37,0:20:27.12,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to answer her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:28.54,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.54,0:20:32.17,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,People have no choice but \Nto answer her question.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.42,0:20:33.46,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Just one question...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:38.17,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Who is... Sasa Kazamori?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.59,0:20:40.72,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.22,0:20:45.64,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Who?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.28,0:21:01.86,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,There never was...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.20,0:21:03.49,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.87,0:21:07.20,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,There never was a human \NKazamori to begin with!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:09.41,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.41,0:21:11.67,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Kazamori wasn't human.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.46,0:21:14.75,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Kazamori?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:19.01,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,The cat's out of the bag...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.01,0:21:20.05,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,The cat's out of the bag... :)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.60,0:21:36.15,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,In the pale morning mist, a whispered prayer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.52,0:21:44.16,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna follow this twisted landscape with you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.62,0:21:52.16,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for the "truth", "a 'lie' will do" is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.50,0:22:00.55,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Tracing it as if we can see through
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.55,0:22:04.47,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for, beyond words
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.47,0:22:08.47,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Like a falling feather
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.47,0:22:11.48,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for, find it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.39,0:22:16.90,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,So we can cuddle close together here
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.20,0:22:36.33,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for, unravel it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:40.46,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Like a tattered cloud
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.46,0:22:43.30,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for, find it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.18,0:22:48.51,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,So we can cuddle close together here
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.64,0:22:53.81,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,The original work for next time is the \Nsame as this time, "Masked Mansion".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.81,0:22:55.48,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not all...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.48,0:22:57.81,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,A story called "Shoplifting \NFamily" is in there too?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.81,0:22:59.52,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give it a read!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.52,0:23:00.48,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.48,0:23:02.94,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,It's like in this old family, \Nthere are all these members
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.94,0:23:06.49,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,and people connected to them, and \Neveryone has a hidden secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.49,0:23:10.66,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,This story is kind of similar to ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.66,0:23:14.41,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me Ango-sensei \Nhas gone to all this trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.41,0:23:18.27,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,so he can blow the whistle \Non sharing ideas!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.27,0:23:20.53,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,I like that kind of meanness!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.53,0:23:22.56,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,So anyway, next time on UN-GO:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.32,0:23:24.31,Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,"House, {\b1}Unmasked{\b0}"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.32,0:23:24.31,Source,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Inspired by Ango Sakaguchi’s\NMeijikaika Ango Torimonochou\N(Meiji-era Ango Detective Stories)\N"Shoplifting Family", "Masked Mansion"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.56,0:23:23.69,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,House, Unmasked!
